  "description": "<p>A supernatural sign of corruption occurs when a horror or otherworldly being is responsible for the corruption. The corrupted Ironlander takes on some characteristic of that being or its realm of origin. While these signs can sometimes be a tool for the Ironlander to use (such as a monstrous ability), they are more often a disturbing reminder to themselves and others of the dark force at work within them.</p>",
